S.FORM: Kingdalruwane Itiniay i Sandimen Cen no Pingtung ko Kingdalruwane a niyaro', 17 ko sa'osi no parod no loma', 62 ko sa'osi no tamdaw. 98 ko ka'aloman no Yincomin, polong han i, 61 ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 2 ko ka'aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 1 ko tamdaw. O pa sin to no ka'aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Rukai66 , Paiwan21 , roma11 .
